The '''1249th Mobile Corps''' was a [[mobile corps]] of the [[Imperial Army/Legends|Imperial Army]] that operated within the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

==History==
During the battle for control of the [[Kalinda system/Legends|Kalinda system]] several [[Standard year/Legends|years]] after the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], the 1249th supported the [[2391st Battle Squadron]].

